Package: hdIndep
Type: Package
Title: Bootstrap Test for Independence Testing in High Dimensions
Description: This R package implements the block multiplier bootstrap test for pairwise independence of one random variable from a large pool of other random variables. Moreover, this test is combined with a stepdown procedure (Romano-Wolf) for selecting those variables from the pool that violate independence, while controlling for the familiwise error rate. The theory is is developed in Olivares, Olma, and Wilhelm (2025) <https://arxiv.org/pdf/2503.21715#page=1.38>. 
Version: 0.1.0
BugReports: https://github.com/mauolivares/hdIndep/issues
URL: https://github.com/mauolivares/hdIndep
